casebody.data:
No. 16,

Misc.

Bushnell v. Ellis, Corrections Director. Petitioner pro se. Will Wilson, Attorney General of Texas, • and B. H. Timmins, Jr. and Leon F. Pesek, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Criminal Appeals of Texas granted. Case transferred to the appellate docket.
